title: TOMTOM MOSQUES MASJID POI
description:
this torrent has about 1300 mosques from all over the uk for use with tomtom.


the mosques were compiled from the database of the muslim directory 2005 and from the mosque poi file held on www.pocketgps.com using software called poiedit which can be googled.  this software can convert the tomtom file into different formats for use on other satnavs



i travel all the time and whenever im in a different town i always program in any mosque that is not on the database because it only takes a few seconds.

if you see any mosques in your area i would be gratefull if you can write them below so the database can be kept up to date.

jazakallah khair
